#. Tag: para
#: sle_update_preparation.xml:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a package has been split, all new packages are installed in the upgrade case to retain the same functionality as the previous version. However, the new default for a fresh installation of &slea;&nbsp; <replaceable>X+1</replaceable> may be to not install all packages."
