"&prompt.sudo;SUSEConnect --list-extensions | grep LTSS\n"
"SUSE Linux Enterprise Server LTSS 12 SP4 x86_64 (Installed)\n"
"Deactivate with: SUSEConnect -d -p SLES-LTSS/12.4/x86_64"
